(41, 14, 12, 46, 5, 7, 8, 'the passover', 'Passover and Unleavened Bread Connection', 'This connection highlights the significance of Passover in both passages. Mark 14:12 refers to the preparation of the Passover, while 1 Corinthians 5:7-8 emphasizes Christ as the Passover sacrifice and the call to be unleavened, linking the themes of purity and sacrifice.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
